  "short_description": "TransPort Power System, 1x 10/100 MbE RJ45 Port, 1x Power TransPort output, 115Wh Li-ion backup battery",
  "description": "UISP-P is an uninterruptible power system designed for MicroPoP applications. The power system is equipped with two slots for 120W Power TransPort Adapters, DC battery port for 24VDC 8.33A lead acid battery (the battery is not included), the battery bay for rechargeable Li-Ion battery with included battery and the Power TransPort output port. The UISP-P power system provides 27VDC 100W output power using one TransPort adapter and 27VDC 200W output power with two TransPort adapters. The UISP-P power system is compatible with UISP Console, UISP Router (installed with UISP Box), UISP Router Pro, UISP Switch (installed with UISP Box), UISP Switch Pro. UISP-P is wall-mountable, the wall mounting kit is included. The power system is managed with the UISP application: Version 1.4.5 and later.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Uninterruptible Power System",
      "text": "UISP-P is an uninterruptible power system designed for MicroPoP applications. The power system is equipped with two slots for 120W Power TransPort Adapters, DC battery port for 24VDC 8.33A lead acid battery (the battery is not included), the battery bay for rechargeable Li-Ion battery with included battery and the Power TransPort output port. The UISP-P power system provides 27VDC 100W output power using one TransPort adapter and 27VDC 200W output power with two TransPort adapters."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Compatibility and Management",
      "text": "The UISP-P power system is compatible with UISP Console, UISP Router (installed with UISP Box), UISP Router Pro, UISP Switch (installed with UISP Box), UISP Switch Pro. UISP-P is wall-mountable, the wall mounting kit is included. The power system is managed with the UISP application: Version 1.4.5 and later."
    }
  ],
